; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496470763117395.png\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25.6px;\">　　本届竞赛节与武术节一同吹响号角，设有少林拳项目、国际竞赛规定项目、其他传统项目和集体项目四大竞赛项目，共342个小项。我校学员共获得47块金牌，63块银牌，29块铜牌，让我们一起去感受一下这激动人心的时刻吧。</span></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496470763476964.png\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25.6px;\">　让我们再次祝贺他们，希望在未来可以更上一层楼，再创佳绩!</span></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496470764771129.png\"/></span></span></p><p><br/></p>','/Public/Uploads/59325526c0469.png','2017-05-26','少林资讯','美国,中产阶级,为什么,不买,奢侈品,值得,',20,''),(17,'武术节完美收官，武僧学院学员喜获47金','武术节完美收官，武僧学院学员喜获47金','<p><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">少林武术节的竞赛在激烈的比拼中结束，为期四天的郑州少林国际武术节也在一声声真诚的告别中，缓缓落下帷幕。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">嵩山少林寺武僧学院教育集团</span><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">的学员们在本届武术节中勇创佳绩。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496470719116396.png\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25.6px;\">　　本届竞赛节与武术节一同吹响号角，设有少林拳项目、国际竞赛规定项目、其他传统项目和集体项目四大竞赛项目，共342个小项。我校学员共获得47块金牌，63块银牌，29块铜牌，让我们一起去感受一下这激动人心的时刻吧。</span></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496470719638849.png\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25.6px;\">　让我们再次祝贺他们，希望在未来可以更上一层楼，再创佳绩!</span></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25.6px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496470719447057.png\"/></span></span></p><p><br/></p>','/Public/Uploads/593254c270047.png','2017-06-02','少林资讯','武术节完美收官，武僧学院学员喜获47金',6,''),(18,'少林足球队的小女子们~','少林足球队的小女子们~','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">足球，充满激情与魅力的字眼，在中国，绝大部分人认为，它是属于男生的运动，足球场上的潇洒过人、奋勇搏击，挥洒汗水……女生一样也可以!</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463720175698.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　今天就带大家一起走进嵩山少林寺武僧学院教育集团少林足球队，看看少林小女子们的风采吧!</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　她们中，有明眸皓齿的精灵，有长发飘飘的淑女，有可爱呆萌的开心果，有让人只能望其项背的高冷妹，也有奔跑着像风一样的女子……</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463720563716.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463721833955.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463721798669.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463721975659.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　看着女孩子们在球场上奔跑，欢笑，拼搏，就能瞬间捕捉到一种神奇的力量，走上球场，淑女一秒变身女汉子!那种自信从容、挥洒自如，分分钟秒杀男生，让人不禁想喊出一个字——“帅”!</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463721886110.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463721103809.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463722257631.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　高聪教练是这支女子足球队的教练，话语不多的她在教学时迸发出的人格魅力是无人能敌的。言传身教、身体力行，胜过千言万语!</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463722106899.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　冯巧，和她的名字一样，乖巧可爱，一个12岁像风一样的贵州姑娘，来武僧团训练已经很久了，她说自己热爱足球，热爱运动，每天来训练就是最快乐的。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463722527311.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463722963825.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　“我练武术套路已经一年多了，我们还会使用棍、枪和剑。” 少林足球队的女生们说。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463722121297.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　姑娘们可是人人都会武术哦，瞧，一字马棒棒哒!</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463722509969.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　这也是少林足球队的特色，武术与足球运动并重，推进少林武术与青少年足球运动的深度融合，在锻炼意志的同时培养技能。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463723882065.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p>','/Public/Uploads/593239ee46cc2.png','2017-06-02','媒体新闻','少林足球队的小女子们~',16,''),(19,'来访 | “一带一路”11国代表团，来武僧学院看了','来访 | “一带一路”11国代表团，来武僧学院看了','<h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5月14日，“一带一路”国际合作高峰论坛在北京如期举行。5月11日，武僧学院教育集团原河南大学副校长、集团校长史全生教授及全体师生隆重欢迎了“一带一路”伊斯坦布尔代表团的到来。</span><br/><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463283705376.jpg\"/><br/><br/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　武僧学院教育集团热情接待了阿富汗、哈萨克斯坦、吉尔吉斯斯坦、土耳其、伊朗、巴基斯坦、塔吉克斯坦、土库曼斯坦、沙特阿拉伯、阿塞拜疆及阿联酋等伊斯坦布尔进程11国代表团。</span><br/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　武僧学院教育集团大力支持“一带一路”战略，伊斯坦布尔进程是重要的涉阿富汗问题地区合作平台，也是“一带一路”战略中重要的项目平台。</span><br/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　11国代表团在史全生校长的引领下，参观了校园，随后来到武僧学院教育集团禅武堂观看了表演队学员们精彩绝伦的少林功夫表演。</span><br/><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463283770311.jpg\"/><br/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　贵宾们对学员们精彩绝伦的少林功夫表演给予了高度的评价，并表示少林功夫是中国文化的代表，一定要发扬和传承下去!</span><br/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　通过此次的友好访问，不仅促进了少林武术的传播与交流，也进一步增强了“一带一路”倡议对周边国家的感召力，促进了地区互联互通合作。</span><br/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　演出结束后，代表团与史全生校长及学员们合影留念。武僧学院教育集团积极响应国家的政策，在“一带一路”国际合作高峰论坛召开之际，在此预祝论坛峰会取得圆满成功!</span><br/><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496463284865799.jpg\"/></h2><br/>','/Public/Uploads/593237f49cc11.jpg','2017-06-02','武校新闻','来访 | “一带一路”11国代表团，来武僧学院看了',18,''),(20,'集团教练员培训启动，热闹背后看实效！','集团教练员培训启动，热闹背后看实效！','<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496464046101051.png\"/></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;为了建设一支师德高尚、业务精湛、结构合理、充满活力的高素质教练员队伍，进一步深化武术专业课教育，全面提升教育教学质量，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　嵩山少林寺武僧学院教育集团</span><span style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">启动了教练员业务培养计划。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: medium; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496464046836882.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　本次培训聘请了登封市体育局工会主席郑跃峰，武林风裁判、国家一级裁判马涛为教练员培训讲师。其中马涛老师曾是轰动一时的泰拳王播求与少林武僧一龙《世纪之战2》场上裁判，“武林风”各项比赛中执法十几年，有着丰富的武术裁判经验。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496464046730550.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　加强对武术运动的理解，掌握武术教学的理论知识、技术和技能，提高教学能力和管理水平，达到《标准》中各级武术体育教练员在理论知识和技能方面的基本要求，为参加相应的等级职业技能鉴定考试做好准备。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496464046114585.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　各位培训老师完备的教学大纲，充实的学习内容，生动有趣的讲解让教练员们的职业技能培训获得了收获和惊喜。纸上得来终觉浅，绝知此事要躬行。相信通过培训，他们都能成为一名优秀的教练.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496464047426100.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　汗水，是浇灌增长知识的甘露，</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　刻苦，是通向武术宝库的桥梁;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　交流，是走向成熟教学的捷径;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　知识，是不断完善自我的妙法;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　责任，是必须肩负承担的义务。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496464047140425.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　古语有云：“台上一分钟，台下十年功”，这是一次具有深远意义的培训!不仅明确了集团武术运动发展的方向.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496464047668584.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　希望此次培训对集团武术教练员在人生的里程碑上，能够留下浓墨重彩的一笔!</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170603/1496464047979059.png\"/></p><p><br/></p>','/Public/Uploads/59323ab09f72f.png','2017-06-03','媒体新闻','集团教练员培训启动，热闹背后看实效！',16,''),(21,'少林寺首届无遮大会之《黑白决》实施方案','尧造围棋以开天地之象，佛传禅宗以澈万化之先。','<p>尧造围棋以开天地之象，佛传禅宗以澈万化之先。当年的神仙是否依旧、烂柯的棋局谁人重演。兰亭雅会不见当年王谢。秦宫汉墓刻画了多少纵横。骚人狂客、夜覆血泪之篇；当湖争霸、至今犹称独步。从来名山藏名刹、自古高士留名局。千载争霸俱往矣，风流今朝在少林。</p>','/Public/Uploads/59326a1421330.png','2017-06-03','武校新闻','',21,''),(22,'2017年少林寺都市禅堂浴佛节放生祈福法会的通知','佛诞节也称“浴佛节”,是纪念释迦牟尼佛的重大节日。','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">佛诞节也称“浴佛节”,是纪念释迦牟尼佛的重大节日。据《过去现在因果经》卷一的记载,印度迦毗罗卫国王后摩耶夫人,在蓝毗尼花园的无忧树下,诞生了悉达多太子,太子周行七步一手指天一手指地发出“天上天下,唯我独尊”的宣言,随即从空中直泻下两条银涟似的净水沐浴在太子的身上。佛弟子们为庆祝和纪念佛陀诞辰就沿用此形式举行“浴佛仪式”。</span></p>','/Public/Uploads/59326b6b80d09.png','2017-06-03','武校新闻','',18,''),(23,'少林七十二艺选拔赛竞赛规则少林七十二艺选拔赛竞赛规则','少林七十二艺，是对少林弟子和坊间习练流传的与少林相关的武艺内容的俗称，包罗万象，内容丰富。','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">少林七十二艺，是对少林弟子和坊间习练流传的与少林相关的武艺内容的俗称，包罗万象，内容丰富。每一种技艺均需反复习练和实践以达到身心一体、禅武合一的修行效果。学习和交流少林功夫，是对少林文化的传承与发展。<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">少林七十二艺，是对少林弟子和坊间习练流传的与少林相关的武艺内容的俗称，包罗万象，内容丰富。每一种技艺均需反复习练和实践以达到身心一体、禅武合一的修行效果。学习和交流少林功夫，是对少林文化的传承与发展。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">少林七十二艺，是对少林弟子和坊间习练流传的与少林相关的武艺内容的俗称，包罗万象，内容丰富。每一种技艺均需反复习练和实践以达到身心一体、禅武合一的修行效果。学习和交流少林功夫，是对少林文化的传承与发展。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">少林七十二艺，是对少林弟子和坊间习练流传的与少林相关的武艺内容的俗称，包罗万象，内容丰富。每一种技艺均需反复习练和实践以达到身心一体、禅武合一的修行效果。学习和交流少林功夫，是对少林文化的传承与发展。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">少林七十二艺，是对少林弟子和坊间习练流传的与少林相关的武艺内容的俗称，包罗万象，内容丰富。每一种技艺均需反复习练和实践以达到身心一体、禅武合一的修行效果。学习和交流少林功夫，是对少林文化的传承与发展。</span></span></p>','/Public/Uploads/59326e571f199.png','2017-06-03','武校新闻','',15,''),(24,'“五一”少林寺皈依法会通启','为方便大众认识佛教、学习佛法、亲近三宝、获得利益，都市禅堂特别开设“皈依学习培训班”这一学习和皈依的通道','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">为方便大众认识佛教、学习佛法、亲近三宝、获得利益，都市禅堂特别开设“皈依学习培训班”这一学习和皈依的通道，使得大家有机会亲闻佛法道理，让我们明明白白皈依，堂堂正正做人，清清楚楚修行，望各位善士踊跃报名，早证菩提！具体事项如下</span></p>','/Public/Uploads/59326efe2b714.png','2017-06-03','学院军训','',19,''),(25,'暨中华传统医药传承与未来及中国药文化研究会发展年会','论文征集启示','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">千年古刹嵩山少林自古以禅、医、武闻名于世，并作为中华民族优秀文化代表之一，已成为具有真实性、独特性和唯一性的人类文化遗产，具有极强的国际号召力。<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">有“中国佛门医宗”之誉的少林药局始建于公元</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">1217</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">年，在历代高僧不断的钻研和努力下，形成独特的佛医禅药体系：三疗七修造福当下。</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">2011</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">年</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">5</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">月，在少林寺的倡导下，举办了“首届中国佛医高峰论坛”。</span></span></p>','/Public/Uploads/59326f42c4fd1.png','2017-06-03','学院军训','',8,''),(26,'少林寺举办丁酉年世界传灯祈福法会通启','少林寺举办丁酉年世界传灯祈福法会通启少林寺举办丁酉年世界传灯祈福法会通启','<p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">“灯”是佛门六种供具之一，用灯来供养佛菩萨三宝。以“一灯能破千年暗”为象征，通过“灯灯相传，传灯无尽”传递美好的愿望。点亮了真理和慈悲的明灯，从此，苦海里的众生有了希望。象征智慧光明的心灯，象征了佛法的薪火相传。</p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">《般若经》云：“诸佛弟子凡有所说，一切皆承佛威神力，与诸法性常不相违。依所说法，精勤修学，证法实性，故佛所言如灯传照。”</p><p><br/></p>','/Public/Uploads/59326fb920de9.png','2017-06-03','学院军训','',17,''),(27,'丁酉年少林寺水陆大法会第六天 礼大忏悔文，供下堂1','丁酉年少林寺水陆大法会第六天 礼大忏悔文，供下堂丁酉年少林寺水陆大法会第六天 礼大忏悔文，供下堂','<p><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">【本网讯】</strong></span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">2017</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">年</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">6</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">月</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">2</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">日，农历</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">五</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">月</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">初八</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">，</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">丁酉</span><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">年少林寺水陆大法会进入第六天，内坛举行礼大忏悔文、上佛供、供下堂等，外坛各坛坛口分别拜忏、诵经、念佛、延生回向等。</span></p>','/Public/Uploads/5932890417304.png','2017-06-03','媒体新闻','',20,''),(28,'美国洛杉矶少林文化中心负责人延续法师受邀前往欧洲传播少林文化','美国洛杉矶少林文化中心负责人延续法师受邀前往欧洲传播少林文化','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(167, 169, 170);\">这次欧洲巡回讲座，得到了许多当地武术组织和禅修组织的赞赏与支持，并与奥地利少林文化中心、英国少林修文化中心等海外少林文化中心合作，交流学习心得，传播少林文化。</span></p>','/Public/Uploads/5934b9b24e0b4.png','2017-06-03','学院军训','asd',33,''),(29,'丁酉年少林寺水陆大法会第五天 斋天法会庄严举行','丁酉年少林寺水陆大法会第五天 斋天法会庄严举行丁酉年少林寺水陆大法会第五天 斋天法会庄严举行','<p>【本网讯】2017年6月1日，农历四五月初七，丁酉年少林寺水陆大法会进入第五天。当日，内坛告赦、诵《地藏经》、上佛供、请下堂、授幽冥戒。外坛举行斋天法会、拜忏、诵经、念佛、延生回向等，以敬上慈下，悲济群生，普同受利。</p><p>凌晨三点，告赦仪式在法会内坛举行，坛内诸师及功德主奉请梵释二天捷疾持赦使者，携带赦书、赦牒，上达梵天与帝释天，下至地府及城隍土境，向帝释天、阎王与土地神祗陈情，希望能让六道之中受苦受难的群灵得赦通行，前往水陆坛场接受斋供，听闻佛法，发菩提心，永脱幽途，转生净土。</p><p><br/></p>','/Public/Uploads/5936285894434.png','2017-06-03','少林资讯','111',37,'wen'),(30,'河南少林寺武校的毕业证书受到社会的认可？','河南登封嵩山少林寺武术学校-招生对象.态度端正、身体健康、有毅力、爱好武术,年龄在3-25周岁的男女青少年,不限国籍。     虽然现在武术行业发展比较好，就业机会比较多，但是这个社会的大多数工作还是要看文凭的，所以好多家长们在担心孩子在少林寺武校学习武术后，其毕业证书不会受到社会的认可，在那里犹豫不决到底要不要让孩子学习武术。那么河南少林寺武校毕业的学员，其颁发的毕业证书有用吗？受到社会的认可吗？今天我们嵩山少林寺武术学校招生办的老师就给大家讲解一下，让家长们和学员们吃一颗定心丸。','<p><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 河南登封嵩山少林寺武术学校-招生对象.态度端正、身体健康、有毅力、爱好武术,年龄在3-25周岁的男女青少年,不限国籍。</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 虽然现在武术行业发展比较好，就业机会比较多，但是这个社会的大多数工作还是要看文凭的，所以好多家长们在担心孩子在少林寺武校学习武术后，其毕业证书不会受到社会的认可，在那里犹豫不决到底要不要让孩子学习武术。那么河南少林寺武校毕业的学员，其颁发的毕业证书有用吗？受到社会的认可吗？今天我们<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"http://www.shaolinzongban.com/zsjz.html\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;\">嵩山少林寺武术学校招生办</a></strong>的老师就给大家讲解一下，让家长们和学员们吃一颗定心丸。</p><p><img alt=\"少林寺武术学校的学员在练习武术\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170612/1497237060990333.jpg\"/></p><p>　　河南少林寺武术学校是一所正规、公办的少林寺武术学校。少林寺武术学校的开办是经过了国家的批准和少林寺的扶持。所以不管是少林寺武术学校的教育体系，还是所颁发的毕业证书也都是得到国家的认可的。因此，在河南少林寺武术学校毕业以后学校所颁发的毕业证书不管是在国家教育局的档案当中，还是在用人单位都是得到认可的。请家长们放心让孩子在河南少林寺武术学校学习。</p><p>　　为了能够弘扬少林寺的武术和精神，河南少林寺武术学校常年对外招生，只要年龄满3-25周岁，身体健康，没有传染性疾病、先天性疾病或者重大疾病，并且热爱武术，都是有机会到河南少林寺武术学校来学习的。不过并不是每一位到学校报名的学员都能够成功的进入到少林寺武术学校的。想要进入到少林寺武术学校需要经过学校的面试和体检，只有合格的学员才能够成功进入到少林寺武术学校学习正宗的少林武术。</p><p><img alt=\"少林寺武术学校的学员在练习武术\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170612/1497237060163262.jpg\"/></p><p>　　在河南少林寺武术学校学习，学员在毕业以后都会是能文能武的全能型人才，所以每一位从少林寺武术学校毕业的学员都能够在未来有更多的选择。学校也会帮助学员，为学员提供更多的就业机会的。不管学员未来想要往哪个方向去发展，学校都会为我们优秀的学员去铺路的。想要孩子的未来有无线的可能性，想要孩子的未来能够有更多的发展，那么就到河南少林寺武术学校来学习正宗的少林武术吧！</p><p><br/></p>','/Public/Uploads/593e0658a48d6.png','2017-06-12','媒体新闻','河南少林寺武校的毕业证书受到社会的认可？',82,'sun'),(31,'最好的少林寺招生官网有什么特征呢?','近些年来，少林武术深受人们的喜爱，学武的人多了，各种武术培训学校也在不断增多，这么多的学校，最好的少林寺武校有什么特征呢?一所优秀的学校，肯定有完备的硬件设施、一流的教学质量、雄厚的师资力量、和谐美好的校园环境，而少林寺旗下的少林寺武校完全做到了以上几点。我校每年投入大量资金用于学校建设上，除了这些，最好的少林寺武校不仅仅只是如此。','<p>近些年来，少林武术深受人们的喜爱，学武的人多了，各种武术培训学校也在不断增多，这么多的学校，最好的少林寺武校有什么特征呢?一所优秀的学校，肯定有完备的硬件设施、一流的教学质量、雄厚的师资力量、和谐美好的校园环境，而少林寺旗下的少林寺武校完全做到了以上几点。我校每年投入大量资金用于学校建设上，除了这些，最好的少林寺武校不仅仅只是如此。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><br/>&nbsp;</p><p>　　1、好的少林寺武校能够保证每个学员都能学到真正的少林功夫。我们少林寺武校教练由少林武僧及俗家弟子组成，每位教练都拥有丰富的教学经验，并对学生采用小班授课、面对面指导，针对不同学员采用不同的教学方式，还会定期进行测试，及时帮助学生找漏补缺。</p><p>　　2、好的少林寺武校讲究科学的教育方式。在少林寺武校，学生是进行文武教育的，一天之中是半天文化课，半天武术课，可以让学生合理安排学习及休息的时间，有效做到劳逸结合。在进行武术训练时，对于初学者，教练们会先教学员练习少林基本功，快速全面提高身体素质，然后再进行套路训练。</p><p>　　3、好的少林寺武校重视毕业学员的就业问题。我校不仅为考试合格的毕业学员颁发相应的证书，同时还会为学员推荐就业渠道。学员们都可根据自己的特长选择就业，还可以到体校深造，或参加入伍当兵，还可以考入司法武警、公安院校，还可进入影视圈做演员等等，减轻学生就业负担。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><br/>&nbsp;</p><p>　　嵩山少林寺武校是最好的武术学校，是少林寺旗下的学校，还是国家公办的学校，文武兼修的教学模式得到家长们的一致认可，且封闭式寄宿式管理模式让家长们更放心送孩子来这里上学。少林寺武校是真真正正的一所青少年儿童武术培训院校，随时欢迎各位来校考察，有任何问题还可咨询招生办老师。</p><p><br/></p>','/Public/Uploads/593e06b0c0e1e.png','2017-06-12','少林资讯','最好的少林寺招生官网有什么特征呢?',60,'sun'),(32,'河南嵩山少林寺文武招生官网是怎么收费的？一','学习武术对自身有很多的好处，比如可以强身健体、锻炼人的毅力、精神和心理素质，这也是很多家长送孩子到河南少林寺武术学校上学的原因之一。最近几年随着武术行业的兴起，越来越多的人意识到学习武术有一个好身体的重要性，随着也带动了武术学校不断增多，眼下学习武术已经成为一种潮流。想要学习正宗的少林功夫，就到国家公办、少林寺直属的武术学校上学，在这里收费标准是根据省教育厅规定，绝对不会出现乱收费现象，那么河南公办少林寺武术学校每年是怎么收费的？一年要花多少钱呢？','<p>学习武术对自身有很多的好处，比如可以强身健体、锻炼人的毅力、精神和心理素质，这也是很多家长送孩子到河南少林寺武术学校上学的原因之一。最近几年随着武术行业的兴起，越来越多的人意识到学习武术有一个好身体的重要性，随着也带动了武术学校不断增多，眼下学习武术已经成为一种潮流。想要学习正宗的少林功夫，就到国家公办、少林寺直属的武术学校上学，在这里收费标准是根据省教育厅规定，绝对不会出现乱收费现象，那么河南公办少林寺武术学校每年是怎么收费的？一年要花多少钱呢？</p><p>　　选择不同的班级其收费标准是有一定的差别的。现在在河南少林寺武术学校的班级主要有普通班、中托班、高级全托班，下面是不同班级的收费标准，家长们可以根据孩子的自理能力和年龄来选择不同的班级：<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><br/>&nbsp;</p><p>　　1. 普通班：学费一年12000元，适合13周岁以上，有一定自理能力的孩子，系我校的标准班级。此费用包含学费、普通标准伙食费、服装被褥、水电费、文化课学杂费、住宿费</p><p>　　2. 中托班：学费一年16800元，有一定自理能力的孩子，系我校的中端班级。此费用包含学费、全托标准伙食费、服装被褥、水电费、文化课学杂费、住宿费。</p><p>　　3. 高级全托班：学费一年18900元，适合7—12周岁之间的孩子，系我校的高端班级，有专门的生活老师照顾，有人洗衣服。此费用包含学费、全托标准伙食费、护理费、体检保险费、洗澡费、服装被褥、水电费、文化课学杂费、住宿费。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><br/>&nbsp;</p><p>　　现在已经进入了2017年5月份，夏季招生时间已经开始，欢迎全国武术爱好者和家长们前来考察和报名，数量有限名额报满为止，想要学习少林功夫的学员可以与我校招生办老师提前联系报名，嵩山少林寺武术学校招生报名电话：13073775500</p><p><br/></p>','/Public/Uploads/593e06f50e646.png','2017-06-12','少林资讯','河南嵩山少林寺文武招生官网是怎么收费的？一',116,'sun');
